DUBAI: Driving in Baghdad is an eventful experience most of the time, but even the most experienced local motorists were left somewhat amazed when they saw a lion leaning out of a car window. The jaw-dropping moment was captured on video and has been doing the rounds on social media ever since. اسد يطل برأسه من نافذة سيارة صاحبه متجولا في أحد شوارع العاصمة #بغداد pic.twitter.com/uPdFR8Pgn6 — مؤسسة المدى (@madanewspaper) April 23, 2022 But not all have reacted favorably to the shocking sight, with some saying the lion’s owner had shown a “disregard for other peoples’ lives” by taking the wild animal on a car ride. Others called on the authorities to intervene and to punish the driver.